                        | Android Application Engineer
                    p.lead.mb-5
                        span.d-block.mb-3
                            | Former Android Engineer at LY Corporation, where I drove the development of "Yahoo! Car Navigation" and "Yahoo! Maps" from requirement definition to performance optimization. In June 2026, I joined Sumitomo Mitsui Card Company.
                        span.d-block.mb-3
                            | Passionate about mobility tech, location-based services, and FinTech UX.
                        span.d-block.mb-2
                            strong Open to Part-time / Side Opportunities
                        span.d-block
                            | ・Availability: 1–2 days/week (approx. 8–16 hours/week)
                        span.d-block.mb-3
                            | ・Work Style: Fully Remote
                        span.d-block.mb-2
                            strong Languages:
                        span.d-block
                            | ・Japanese (Native)
                        span.d-block
                            | ・Chinese (Native)
                        span.d-block
                            | ・English (Business)
                    .social-icons
                        a.social-icon(href='mailto:bryant@ymail.ne.jp', aria-label='Email')
                            i.fas.fa-envelope
                        a.social-icon(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/%E5%A2%A8%E6%B6%B5-%E8%BE%BA-031a8a394/')
                            i.fab.fa-linkedin-in
                        a.social-icon(href='https://github.com/henbryant')
                            i.fab.fa-github

